<div class="text-white text-3xl">2. Reveal programming task</div>

<main class="text-white">
  <%= form_tag(students_task_path) do %>
    <p class="text-white mt-6">
      To apply for the fellowship, you have to build a command-line program and submit its code for review.
    </p>

    <p class="text-white mt-6">
      It is not an algorithmic challenge, and does not have any hidden complexity. Think of it as just an enjoyable
      programming session.</p>

    <p class="text-white mt-6">
      You can spend anywhere from 5 hours to 2 days to write and submit this program.
    </p>

    <p class="text-white mt-6">
      <strong>Once you reveal the problem description, you should finish and submit the code within 2 days.</strong>
    </p>

    <p class="text-white mt-6">Click the button when you're ready!</p>

    <p>
      <%= submit_tag "Reveal programming problem", data: { confirm: "We're excited to see what you make! But make sure you have at least a day to spend on this problem. So, are we ready?" }, class: 'mt-6 block text-center px-10 py-4 bg-gray-900 text-primary-500 border border-primary-500 font-bold font-montserrat rounded shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-primary-900 hover:text-gray-900 transition duration-250 ease-in-out' %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
</main>
